page_0:
"It whispers to me at night.

\"Fuquan,\" it says, \"you must bring me to your brethren in the Necropolis. But before that, you must make sure nobody can leave Caerul.\"

Fear swallows my voice, and I cannot answer.

\"You will do as I command,\" it says.

Then it laughs

and laughs

AND LAUGHS"
